{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother had a brother here who came in 1938.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she kept saying to my father, why don't we pick up and go to America?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I recall hearing my father say, I cannot do that, because my children will become, quote-unquote, 'shkotzim and shiksas.' Have to translate?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Please.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A 'shegetz' is a Gentile boy, and a 'shiksa' is a Gentile girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't mean to say anything against the Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What he wanted to say is that we would forget about our religion, and we will get assimilated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he rather took his chances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Romanian until 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wasn't aware of any particular shift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- as far as I recall, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like I said, I don't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know we went on with our lives as usual, until we heard these terrible stories happening in Poland, after Hitler went into Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and so I guess my mother was living in dread and-- and fearing the worst, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that went on for a while, until it came true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what is your memory of the time, the day, that it came true-- the day that the worst happened?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first we were in the ghetto--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were moved into the ghetto-- I couldn't tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say it was two month earlier, three month earlier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Earlier than they took us away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, they took us away in, um-- I think it was May--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And prior to that, it must have been about two, three months that the Germans came into town.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
